<view class="survey-page data-v-26cd614c"><view class="survey-header data-v-26cd614c"><text class="survey-title data-v-26cd614c">🎯 满意度调研</text><text class="survey-subtitle data-v-26cd614c">您的反馈对我们很重要</text></view><view class="survey-form data-v-26cd614c"><view class="form-section data-v-26cd614c"><text class="section-title data-v-26cd614c">1. 整体满意度</text><text class="section-desc data-v-26cd614c">请对我们的社区服务整体满意度进行评价</text><view class="rating-container data-v-26cd614c"><block wx:for="{{5}}" wx:for-item="star" wx:for-index="__i0__" wx:key="*this"><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['setRating',['$0'],[[[5,'',__i0__]]]]]]]}}" class="{{['star','data-v-26cd614c',(rating>=star)?'active':'']}}" bindtap="__e">⭐</text></block></view><text class="rating-text data-v-26cd614c">{{$root.m0}}</text></view><view class="form-section data-v-26cd614c"><text class="section-title data-v-26cd614c">2. 具体服务评价</text><block wx:for="{{services}}" wx:for-item="service" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><view class="service-item data-v-26cd614c"><text class="service-name data-v-26cd614c">{{service.name}}</text><view class="service-rating data-v-26cd614c"><block wx:for="{{5}}" wx:for-item="star" wx:for-index="__i1__" wx:key="*this"><text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['setServiceRating',[index,'$0'],[[[5,'',__i1__]]]]]]]}}" class="{{['small-star','data-v-26cd614c',(service.rating>=star)?'active':'']}}" bindtap="__e">⭐</text></block></view></view></block></view><view class="form-section data-v-26cd614c"><text class="section-title data-v-26cd614c">3. 建议和意见</text><textarea class="suggestion-input data-v-26cd614c" placeholder="请输入您的建议和意见..." maxlength="500" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','suggestion','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{suggestion}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea><text class="char-count data-v-26cd614c">{{$root.g0+"/500"}}</text></view><button class="submit-btn data-v-26cd614c" disabled="{{!canSubmit}}" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['submitSurvey',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e">{{''+submitButtonText+''}}</button></view><block wx:if="{{showSuccessModal}}"><view class="success-modal data-v-26cd614c"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e0',['$event']]]]]}}" class="success-mask data-v-26cd614c" bindtap="__e"></view><view class="success-content data-v-26cd614c"><view class="success-icon data-v-26cd614c">🎉</view><view class="success-title data-v-26cd614c">提交成功！</view><view class="success-desc data-v-26cd614c">感谢您的反馈，积分已发放</view><view class="success-points data-v-26cd614c">{{"+"+points+" 积分"}}</view><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['e1',['$event']]]]]}}" class="success-btn data-v-26cd614c" bindtap="__e"> 知道啦 </button></view></view></block></view>